Corrected the release date. May 1st, 1981 was on a Friday. April 30, 1981 was on a Thursday. Back in the 70s & 80s, films got released theatrically on Fridays and on occasion Wednesdays. The original 1 sheet theatrical poster for the release (which is similar to the one shown on this page) quotes at the bottom “Beginning May 1st.”  Go into IMBD, date is May 1, 1981. Also a movie location site lists it as...May 1, 1981. Check a calendar for dating April/May 1981 for clarification.
